        <h2>
            Joseph Cowen Halls
        </h2>
        <p>The self-catered student residences at Joseph Cowen Halls are perfectly situated in the centre of Newcastle, just a one-minute walk away from the INTO Centre.</p>

        <p>There's a sociable, community environment in the residences, with comfortable shared communal spaces to enjoy with friends. Here you can relax and focus on you studies knowing you're in a safe and secure environment.</p>

